                                        Comparer les Offres
                                    </a>
                                </li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
                                    <a href="/tarifs" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s; font-size: 0.95rem;">
